				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The reason SoE HATES pets is plain and simple, its a 100dps ( in some cases ) 400 mana w/ no focus effects dot, that can tank to an extent
<br />

<br />
the game revolves around mana plain and simple, and with pets we get mana free damage... they dont like that.. so what i propse is this
<br />

<br />
A spell we cast on our current pets to up there damage say to 180-250 dps
<br />
but we still have our base pet when we are lom or melee is gimped for some reason and you need to nuke for more
<br />

<br />
Spell would be something like this
<br />

<br />
Mageairpetspell_01 ( no clue for name ) one for each pet, will use air here
<br />

<br />
Makes pet hit for 180
<br />
proc for 300 ( 6 sec stun )
<br />
have 8k hp with Time focus
<br />
1.5x the Mitigation / avoidance it has now
<br />

<br />
and decreases our mana 150 a tick ( some for of pres effect will need to work with this )
<br />

<br />
lasts till you click off the recourse effect that gets casted on you.
<br />

<br />
