			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have suggested something similar a while ago. Main reason for it: its often the case that you cannot spend all your mana on fights, be it because of aggro restrictions or simply because the fight is too short.
<br />

<br />
Having such a spell that uses up mana to continually to improve the pet might help that, there could even be different versions, one that uses very little mana/tic and gives a small boost to the pet only, or another that drains your mana quickly but turns the pet into a monster for the time.
<br />

<br />
It might be difficult to code, perhaps the spell would be easier to implement to take a fixed amount of mana at once and had a limited duration only. Still think its a pretty good idea, and fairly easy to balance.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=423546" target="_blank" class="postlink">Izudin</a>, 65 Arch Convoker on Quellious</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
